** Block 0: Boot block
*** 00000000 - 000003ff
**** empty
     [[file:./block0.jpg]]
** Block 1: Superblock
*** 00000400 - 000007ff
    [[file:./block1.jpg]]
    
    There are some problems i had in this Block 1
    1. why i had figured out *Filesystem size in blocks* is 1000Byte, not 1024Byte ?
    2. why *block size* and *Fragment size* like this 00 00 00 00 ?
    
