    #+begin_example
    0b 00 00 00 0c 00 01 02
    #+end_example
*** Second entry in /lost+found dir:".."
    #+begin_example
    2e 00 00 00 02 00 00 00
    #+end_example
** Block 38: data block for hello
*** 00009800 - 00009cff
